document_data.caption: A map showing Storaad in western Gwynneth.
document_data.name: Storaad
document_data.mainbody: '''Storaad''' was a small isolated coastal town located on the island of [[Gwynneth]] within the [[Moonshae Isles]].{{Cite interactive atlas}}{{Cite dungeon/196/Backdrop: The Moonshae Isles}}
document_data.Geography: Storaad was found along the coast of the [[Strait of the Leviathan]] in western Gwynneth. It sat among some plains in the shadow of the [[Black Mountains]] which were located to the east.
